fy_a3p_cross_section_mini

This is a medium sized Fight Yard style map inspired by the game A3P. 

I reduced the size of the original from 1.0 scale to 0.65 scale. 

This map can also be used for Gun Game servers.
Enjoy!

-	64 Spawns
-	Nav file for bots
-	Cube Maps
-	3d Skybox
-	Optimized for better FPS
-	Everything is packaged into the .bsp with Pakrat
-	Custom Textures from [-B-]
-	Custom Textures from Eric

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
